Description: Fix SDL2 threading: move rendering to main thread
 SDL2 requires all rendering calls (SDL_RenderPresent, SDL_UpdateTexture,
 SDL_RenderCopy) to happen on the main thread. The previous code used
 SDL_AddTimer which executes the callback on a separate thread, causing
 the black screen and fullscreen toggle glitch.
 .
 Replace SDL_AddTimer with main-loop timing using SDL_GetTicks().
 Demo() becomes a regular void function; Video->Update() is called from
 the main loop after each Demo() call.
 .
 Also fix Init_IDLogo(): add UpdatePalette() after the SetColour() loop so
 the palette is actually applied to Video_Memory before the fade-in starts.
 .
 Also fix Close_Audio(): the FadeOut loop now calls Video->Update() so the
 visual fade-out is rendered.
